## üîé Overview

This is a full-stack web application that enables patients to schedule, reschedule, and cancel appointments with doctors. Doctors can manage their availability, while admins oversee the system through an intuitive interface.

---

## ‚ú® Features

- Patient registration & login  
- Doctor login & schedule management  
- Real-time booking, cancellation, and rescheduling  
- Admin panel for user and appointment management  
- Email/SMS reminders for upcoming appointments  
- Clean and responsive UI across devices  

---

## üõ† Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React.js (or update if different)  
- **Backend:** Node.js + Express.js  
- **Database:** MongoDB / PostgreSQL (update based on your project)  
- **Authentication:** JWT / Sessions  
- **Notifications:** Email / SMS integration  
- **Deployment:** Vercel / Heroku / Netlify  

---

## ‚öôÔ∏è Installation & Setup

### Prerequisites
- Node.js v14+  
- npm or yarn  
- MongoDB or PostgreSQL running locally (or cloud DB)  

### Backend Setup
```bash
cd backend
npm install
cp .env.example .env        # Add your environment variables
npm run start  # Or: npm run dev

cd frontend
npm install
npm start                   # Runs on http://localhost:3000
